@apiUrl        = http://127.0.0.1:5036
@walletAddress = 0x6552556089C196363De67A9F6d244BEEce35d013
@nonce         = {{nonce}}
@signature     = PASTE_SIGNATURE_HERE
@jwt           = {{jwt}}

### 1️⃣  Request a one‑time nonce
POST {{apiUrl}}/authentication/request-nonce
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "{{walletAddress}}"
}

### 2️⃣  — Sign the nonce in your wallet —
# put the resulting signature (0x…) into @signature above

### 3️⃣  Submit signature  →  receive JWT   👈 new route
POST {{apiUrl}}/authentication/submit-signature
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "{{walletAddress}}",
  "signature": "{{signature}}"
}

### 4️⃣  Call a protected endpoint using the JWT
GET {{apiUrl}}/authentication/me
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
